{"tid":688704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[為巴死、為巴亡...]巴膠又在街頭打架！","createTime":"2018-06-03T12:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:57:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"68c84ab9a380a19b3bb875b45db3007862bc2624","tid":688704,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/204712_bc6ab6991927ef3fb32895e036c38045.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F204712_bc6ab6991927ef3fb32895e036c38045.png&h=34f6c788&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/204713_606a897f2bd5adfc1001cf2df30a1ebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F204713_606a897f2bd5adfc1001cf2df30a1ebc.png&h=9c258348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/bkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180603%2Fbkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001.html&d=MjM4JMG%2BNWi3m7oXykWPo10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9a15b661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180603/bkn-20180603201526776-0603_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b73b7ead0fdb79bc3d47a8ac7e35a31a7ffa46b","tid":688704,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"沙田馬場從來是巴士迷的是非之地，繼去年9月有巴士迷在馬場巴士站粗口橫飛兼出手後，今日（3日）又有巴士迷在拍攝馬場巴士時大打出手。網上流出的連環圖顯示，3名少年未知何故，在巴士站附近的空地起爭執，一名紅衣少年疑在跪地求饒，但仍被另外一名少年按在地上打，另一人則在旁附和叫囂。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今日下午，紅衣少年被白衣惡少騎住，再壓在地上，臉向地面。據現場消息指，事件中3人均為巴士迷，被打少年最終被打至出血。有人直指事件涉及巴士迷欺凌，呼籲警方徹查。<br />\n<br />\n巴士迷已不是首次在沙田馬場起爭執。2017年9月馬季開鑼日，至少20名十多歲的巴士迷傍晚在拍攝巴士時，疑有人因故意阻礙其他人拍照，而被其他巴士迷圍住，並以粗口指罵，最終需要警員到場調停，有巴士迷慨嘆:「成個香港巴迷界被你搞『彎』晒啦！」"},{"pid":"dc492ce3a481bcf01e6576a4c3b80324ea60e860","tid":688704,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"啪啪......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/205129_6cf7cd958c5a1e70b698ff92a9dfdd15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F205129_6cf7cd958c5a1e70b698ff92a9dfdd15.png&h=92512541&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/205130_6cf7cd958c5a1e70b698ff92a9dfdd15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F205130_6cf7cd958c5a1e70b698ff92a9dfdd15.png&h=f607ad02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c403659783f9e41ce253c4d797c51498137e001a","tid":688704,"uid":72280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"巴膠示範奪命鉸剪腳 納爾遜式鎖<br />\n（其中一人擬似狗巴兼職站務助理）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/205013_da460abce1aa074e6f400a5201434640.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F205013_da460abce1aa074e6f400a5201434640.png&h=93f9ce1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"524f8b89f18d1d9cd4361104dd247ff09f194e25","tid":688704,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"Gay test"},{"pid":"8c27f507a4b424a6d2b2c6556b4792d9c4314bf4","tid":688704,"uid":17738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:53:50.000Z","msg":"老貓 = 巴膠"},{"pid":"6b869f5136f857e060824f68690cb32ec0edf6ae","tid":688704,"uid":1377,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛靚仔成咁，仲要成班都係"},{"pid":"5eb7e3848c43fe44edb97479b905dbde788583cc","tid":688704,"uid":52581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"屌！影張相咋嘛，洗唔洗打哂交呀？"},{"pid":"8c2cf9a5d76a5393e707149b733798bf4348f06d","tid":688704,"uid":2819,"lik